{"title":"czq的颜色计数","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["2020小学期"],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1213#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/submissions?problem_id=1213","statistics":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1213/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/problem/1213/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.xjtuicpc.com/discussion/problem/1213"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"czq获得了以1号节点为根的一颗五彩缤纷的树，树的每个节点都有一种颜色$c_i$。\r\n\r\nczq对每颗子树都定义了一个“缤纷值”，如果子树中颜色为$j$的节点有$a_j$个，那么将对“缤纷值”产生$a_j^3$的贡献。czq想知道这颗树以每个节点为根的子树的缤纷值。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行一个整数$n$。\r\n\r\n接下来一行有$n$个整数$c_i$，为每个节点的颜色。\r\n\r\n接下来$n-1$行，每行两个整数$u_i,v_i$，为树的边。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出仅一行$n$个整数，为每个节点的“缤纷值”。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"### 样例输入\r\n```\r\n6\r\n1 1 4 5 1 4\r\n1 2\r\n2 3\r\n2 4\r\n3 5\r\n3 6\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 样例输出\r\n```\r\n36 17 9 1 1 1\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1 \\leq n \\leq 10^5$\r\n\r\n$1 \\leq c_i,u_i,v_i \\leq n$"}]}